  "title": "Enrolled Nurse",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary:</strong><br>\nWe are looking for a compassionate and well-presented <strong>Enrolled Nurse</strong> to join our aesthetic plastic surgery clinic. You will assist doctors in clinical procedures, provide patient care, and support light front desk duties when needed.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist doctors during aesthetic and minor surgical procedures</li>\n  <li>Perform pre- and post-treatment care</li>\n  <li>Prepare treatment rooms and ensure hygiene standards</li>\n  <li>Administer medications and monitor patient recovery</li>\n  <li>Educate patients on aftercare and treatment instructions</li>\n  <li>Support front desk with appointment bookings and basic enquiries</li>\n  <li>Maintain patient records and clinic documentation</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Valid registration as an Enrolled Nurse</li>\n  <li>Prior experience in aesthetic, dermatology, or surgical settings preferred</li>\n  <li>Professional grooming and good communication skills</li>\n  <li>Basic computer skills for scheduling and record keeping</li>\n  <li>Friendly, patient, and able to multitask</li>\n</ul>",
